data.enText: a person who takes part in the final of a game or competition

simple_means.memory_skill: final 最后的；决定性的 + ist 从事某职业的人 → 决赛选手

tr: a contestant who reaches the final stages of a competition

value.def: A finalistis someone who reaches the last stages of a competition or tournament by doing well or winning in its earlier stages.

example.ex: The twelve finalists will be listed in the Sunday Times.
example.tran: 12 名决赛选手的名单将刊登在《星期日泰晤士报》上。
